<pb ed="D" xml:id="D62.9026.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead>大悲觀𠀍音菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>至道礼文</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><cb:div type="jing"><lg xml:id="lgD62p0001a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">觀音往昔塵<note n="0001a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">沙【CB】，<g ref="#CB31191"/>【國圖】</note><app n="0001a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">沙</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><g ref="#CB31191"/></rdg></app>刼</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">成佛号曰正覺尊</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">四<g ref="#CB10485"/>誓<g ref="#CB31188"/>慈悲重</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">却𠁅莎婆會普門</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB31188"/><g ref="#CB31188"/>救眾生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">莫逢三<g ref="#CB18926"/>及九橫</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">大悲觀𠀍音菩<g ref="#CB16765"/></l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><lg xml:id="lgD62p0001a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">會中有一菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>起</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">法号名曰無盡意</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">殷勤合掌𥼶迦前</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">為<g ref="#CB22329"/>宣<g ref="#CB22072"/>觀音義</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB31188"/>救眾生莫逢<g ref="#CB18926"/></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">及<note place="inline">九</note>橫大悲觀𠀍</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a06"/><lg xml:id="lgD62p0001a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">尒時佛告盡意</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">觀音<g ref="#CB31188"/>裏難籌𥫫</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">若<unclear/>暫<unclear/>皆得徐</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">必<g ref="#CB31192"/>能令超彼岸</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB31188"/>救眾生莫逢三</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB18926"/>及橫大悲</l></lg>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D62.9026.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><p xml:id="pD62p0002a0101">鐺鍋弟子<g ref="#CB21717"/>略懺煩𢙉鄣<g ref="#CB31192"/>今當次<note n="0002a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">第【CB】，弟【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">第</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">弟</rdg></app>懺悔業
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>能㽵餝𠀍趣在在<g ref="#CB21871"/><g ref="#CB21871"/>是以思惟求離𠀍觧脫所以
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/>六道果報種種不同形類各異當知皆是業力所作以佛
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/>十力中業力甚<g ref="#CB25451"/><g ref="#CB21868"/>夫之人多於此中皆生疑<g ref="#CB17553"/>何以故現
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/>見𠀍<note n="0002a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">間【CB】，問【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">間</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">問</rdg></app>行善之者如是十方盡<g ref="#CB28933"/>空<g ref="#CB30847"/>一切寶弟子<g ref="#CB21717"/><g ref="#CB21717"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/>无始以来至於今日長養煩𢙉日<g ref="#CB25451"/>日厚日滋日茂覆
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>盖慧眼令无所見断除眾善不得相續起鄣不得見佛
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/>不聞正法不值聖僧煩𢙉起鄣不見過去未来一切善
<lb ed="D" n="0002a09"/>𢙣業行是煩𢙉鄣受人天尊貴是煩𢙉鄣生色无
<lb ed="D" n="0002a10"/>色界禪定福樂是煩𢙉鄣不得自在神通飛騰隱
<lb ed="D" n="0002a11"/>顯遍至十方諸佛淨土聴法是煩𢙉鄣學安
<lb ed="D" n="0002a12"/>般<g ref="#CB31189"/><g ref="#CB31189"/><g ref="#CB10830"/>息不淨觀諸煩𢙉鄣學慈慧喜舎
<lb ed="D" n="0002a13"/>因緣是煩𢙉鄣學七方便三<g ref="#CB05136"/>觀是煩𢙉鄣
<lb ed="D" n="0002a14"/>學四念<g ref="#CB21871"/>𤏙頂忍是煩𢙉鄣學聞思<g ref="#CB31190"/>苐一法。</p>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D62.9026.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/><p xml:id="pD62p0003a0101">大德僧聴我比丘某甲當宇十五日宇郍於其中間眀鍾失時兼交
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/>不周絀乱大眾唯<g ref="#CB31188"/>慈悲布施歡喜十五日以滿<g ref="#CB31188"/>眾善
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/>聴大徳僧聴眾善比丘某甲當為十五日宇郍於其中間
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/>𢙢兼交不周<g ref="#CB31188"/>僧之是。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/><p xml:id="pD62p0003a0501">大徳僧聴眾善比丘某甲當為十五日宇郍<note place="inline">三<g ref="#CB22072"/></note>內外監
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/>除上下宇郍。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pD62p0003a0801">𨐌<note n="0003a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">巳【CB】，已【國圖】</note><app n="0003a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">巳</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">已</rdg></app>年正月十日於何法律<g ref="#CB08670"/>法律手上領得官分
<lb ed="D" n="0003a09"/>壹拾伍石玖斗於<g ref="#CB31188"/>僧正<g ref="#CB08670"/>法律冩判官三人
<lb ed="D" n="0003a10"/>手上領得分壹拾八石七斗於啟通上座手上領
<lb ed="D" n="0003a11"/>得分六十八石三斗官通計得粟壹百兩石三斗
<lb ed="D" n="0003a12"/>領得常住粟壹百壹拾伍石<note n="0003a1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">肆【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0003a1201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">肆</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>斗通計粟壹千
<lb ed="D" n="0003a13"/><g ref="#CB30055"/>拾貳石七斗官粟通六百伍拾七石七斗。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a14"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a15"/><p xml:id="pD62p0003a1501"><note n="0003a1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">辛巳【CB】，幸已【國圖】</note><app n="0003a1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">辛巳</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">幸已</rdg></app>年八月七日見過粟陸伯<unclear/>拾六石。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>